### Summary of ASX Announcement:  
**Announcement Type:** Extraordinary General Meeting Results  

- **All resolutions passed**, including:  
  - Ratification of prior share/option issues (Resolutions 1-6)  
  - Approval for new share/option issuances (Resolutions 3A-5)  
  - Share issuance to related parties/fees (Resolutions 7-9)  
- **Voting approval rates:** ~98-99% in favor for all resolutions.  

**No material new capital or operational impacts identified.** Routine approvals for previously disclosed transactions.
